items.name: BlockHashCount
docs: The maximum number of blocks to allow in mortal eras.

items.name: MaximumBlockWeight
docs: The maximum weight of a block.

items.name: DbWeight
docs: The weight of runtime database operations the runtime can invoke.

items.name: BlockExecutionWeight
docs: The base weight of executing a block, independent of the transactions in the block.

items.name: ExtrinsicBaseWeight
docs: The base weight of an Extrinsic in the block, independent of the of extrinsic being executed.

items.name: MaximumBlockLength
docs: The maximum length of a block (in bytes).
